                                <layout style="vertical" rend="arris_up">The ogham inscription runs up the angle of one edge of the stone and round the top. The inscription begins 0.33m from the bottom of the stone and is divided into three sections of eleven, two, and six letters respectively. The first eleven letters of the ogham inscription are divided from the upper letters by an outcrop of quartz (Macalister 1945, 481).</layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
